org.fcrepo.server.security.xacml.pep.rest.filters

Class ObjectsRESTFilterMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fcrepo.server.security.xacml.pep.rest.filters.ObjectsRESTFilterMatcher

  • public class ObjectsRESTFilterMatcher
extends Object
    Formerly ObjectsFilter, this class has been reduced to mapping requests to named RESTFilters. Named filters are mapped to classes in the handlers-objects portion of the config-melcoe-pep.xml file.
    Author:
    nish.naidoo@gmail.com, count0@email.unc.edu
